{"build_type":"library","description":"Fiber category 1: a summation that FAILS at n==2 (to exercise the universal error contract). One cooperative step. pc 0: if n==2 it COMPLETES WITH AN ERROR (result -3, a negative sentinel meaning errored at n=2) and does not recurse; if n<1 base case completes with 0; otherwise launches a child category-1 fiber for n-1 and parks. pc 1 (resumed): if the child result is negative the child FAILED -> this fiber PROPAGATES the same error up (completes with that negative value, does not add) -- receive-from-child, send-up-to-parent; otherwise result = n + child_result. Demonstrates a failure rising through the awaiter graph to the root.","module_name":"advance-failing-summation-fiber-propagating-errors","package_name":"advance-failing-summation-fiber-propagating-errors","function_definitions":{"advance-failing-summation-fiber-propagating-errors":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"s","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"t","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"five","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"eight","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"fifty","variable_type":"i64","assignment_oper